cs.ET, cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.SE 

This paper is likely to belong to the cs.ET (Emerging Technologies) sub-category as it introduces a new programming language for expressing quantum computations. It may also belong to cs.PL (Programming Languages) as it discusses the features of the Quipper language. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) as quantum computing involves the use of logic gates. It may also be relevant to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as quantum computing algorithms are a growing area of research. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.SE (Software Engineering) as it discusses the development of quantum circuits.
